 0/I discs. Such\nhierarchical modelling of disc evolution circumvents the computational\ndifficulty of tracing disc evolution through Class 0/I phase with direct,\nnumerically converged simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Sep 2021 19:02:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
