e radio loudness\nparameter, are not ideal tools for characterising NLS1s. We emphasise the\nnecessity of examining NLS1s as individuals, instead of making assumptions\nbased on their classification. When these issues are properly taken into\naccount, NLS1s offer an exceptional environment to study the interplay of the\nhost galaxy and several AGN-related phenomena, such as jets and outflows.\n[Abstract abridged.]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 10:10:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
