hanging the\nmuscular coordination strategy can strongly affect knee joint forces. Patients\nwith a knee prosthesis may adapt their neuromuscular activation to reduce joint\nforces during locomotion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 11:29:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Nov 2021 15:14:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 19:54:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 3 Jul 2022 14:20:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
