s and inner workings of individual components of the open-domain\ndialogue system Alquist developed within the Alexa Prize Socialbot Grand\nChallenge 4 and the experiments we have conducted to evaluate them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 13:24:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-17"}
