ation across\ndatasets (up to -376.0 MAE and -354.9 MSE) and robustness towards complex\nbackgrounds (up to -10.3 MAE and -16.4 MSE).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 13:51:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 07:57:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-12"}
